{"tid":1890311,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦叉電斷下斷下， 可以點樣解決","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T14:02:36.000Z","uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b63e13e2f0aeecbd0ec885899ecc58edc75de6e4","tid":1890311,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"之前唔見咗原廠舊叉電器<br />\n走左去配<br />\n新嗰個用咗冇幾耐之後<br />\n開始出現低電量叉電嗰陣會斷下斷下<br />\n依家就 一叉就斷下斷下<br />\n<br />\n唔係話叉唔到電<br />\n但係叉住電同用唔到冇咩分別<br />\n佢會係咁彈嗰個叉電logo遮住 mon<br />\n<br />\n用梗 ASUS<br />\n<br />\n想問下電腦問題定係叉電器問題<br />\n使唔使拎電腦去整定係買過一個新嘅叉電器<br />\n自從用咗新嗰個叉電器之後間唔中會出現死機藍mon, 話會幫我重新開啟電腦<br />\n部電腦前年暑假先買<br />\n好驚之後final exam出事"},{"pid":"3125bf679762e960aec87aa51059bd10f35f8541","tid":1890311,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"換個部"},{"pid":"d732e2785a701bc980af9c1a6407082b2e1991c2","tid":1890311,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"叉壞左粒電"},{"pid":"3b2f21f38a2637e3a0fe0f4185f0c1849f8de486","tid":1890311,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d732e2785a701bc980af9c1a6407082b2e1991c2","tid":1890311,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"叉壞左粒電"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"拎去整定要成部電腦換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6326df311839f3c9b1a1f568b0c91fa6e73916be","tid":1890311,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3125bf679762e960aec87aa51059bd10f35f8541","tid":1890311,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"換個部"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"最壞打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dae1264ba328b603d44ca718abe87f10fce684","tid":1890311,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT